    name: "getLinearDamping",
    kind: "method",
    description:
        "Gets the linear damping of the Body.\n\nThe linear damping is the ''rate of decrease of the linear velocity over time''. A moving body with no damping and no external forces will continue moving indefinitely, as is the case in space. A moving body with damping will gradually stop moving.\n\nDamping is not the same as friction - they can be modelled together.",
